snippet.title: Retrowave '84 - Official Demo Announcement Trailer | Realms Deep 2023
snippet.description: Retrowave '84 is a 3D action bullet-time first-person shooter developed by KS98. Complete a variety of objectives within the neon lit art-style while engaging in fast-paced combat against a wide variety of enemies using shotguns, SMGs, and more. Players can also engage bullet-time through jumping allowing for precision shots. Retrowave '84 is launching at a later date for PC with a demo available now.
